    "body": "## Purpose / Description\r\nUsing fragments is preferred over activities for subscreens, so MyAccount.kt is being converted into one\r\n\r\n## Fixes\r\nFixes #13583\r\nRelated #12832 \r\n\r\n## Approach\r\n- Use landscape layouts instead of manual configuration changes check to hide the AnkIDroid logo on small screens\r\n- Create a new LoggedIn fragment to split it from the log-in screen\r\n- Convert MyAccount into a Fragment\r\n- Make LoginActivity a container for the login and logout containers while other activities can't handle fragments well\r\n- Improve some settings that depend on the login result\r\n- Rename MyAccount into LoginFragment\r\n\r\n## How Has This Been Tested?\r\n\r\nSee if the log-in screen looks alright on an Android 13 emulator:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/69634269/234375695-8d4c857d-3e78-4482-b125-a95e13220587.mp4\r\n\r\nAlso tested logging in and out from the preferences screen\r\n\r\n## Learning (optional, can help others)\r\n_Describe the research stage_\r\n\r\n_Links to blog posts, patterns, libraries or addons used to solve this problem_\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n_Please, go through these checks before submitting the PR._\r\n\r\n- [X] You have a descriptive commit message with a short title (first line, max 50 chars).\r\n- [X] You have commented your code, particularly in hard-to-understand areas\r\n- [X] You have performed a self-review of your own code\r\n- [ ] UI changes: include screenshots of all affected screens (in particular showing any new or changed strings)\r\n- [ ] UI Changes: You have tested your change using the [Google Accessibility Scanner](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.accessibility.auditor)\r\n",
